        intellectual-property and privacy rights.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Academic integrity</h2>
    <p>
      Quiz attempts are recorded and may be reviewed by your instructor
      under the FERPA-aligned terms described in the
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. If you are using the Service
      as part of a credit-bearing course, the academic-integrity policies
      of your institution apply in addition to these Terms.
    </p>

    <h2>6. FERPA notice and non-waiver</h2>
